Canonical correlations

Canonical correlation analysis was applied to the 350 facilities with complete process and outcome measures in 2018. For the unranked measures, the largest canonical correlation was 0.25 (p 0.003 by Wilk's lambda). For the ranked measures, the largest correlation was 0.27 (p < 0.001 by Wilk's lambda).
